title: LETS SET THE WORLD ON FIRE | BRAND | Arcanist | Journey to Master

embed.description: Welcome to Arcanist_games's channel on Twitch. Watch them stream League of Legends and other content live and join the community!

replies.body:
Does "unranked to Master" mean that you're a new player but you're excited to try to reach a high rank?

Or does it mean that you already have an account in Master and you've created a smurf to stomp low-MMR players until the system eventually gives you teammates and opponents of your skill level?
I've never gotten to masters, but I made a new account to try and achieve it. So far im in platinum with a 60 something percent winrate! thanks for the question
